<div id="content"><div id="cpad"><h2>Author Bibliographies</h2>

<h3>Publications by Susanne E. Bauer</h3>

<p>This citation list includes papers published while the author has been on staff at the NASA Goddard Institute for Space Studies. It may include some publications based on research conducted prior to their having joined the institute staff.</p>


<h4 id="submitted">Submitted / In Review</h4>
<p>M&uuml;lmenst&auml;dt, J., <span class="gissauthor">A.S. Ackerman</span>, <span class="gissauthor">A.M. Fridlind</span>, M. Huang, P.-L. Ma, N. Mahfouz, <span class="gissauthor">S.E. Bauer</span>, S.M. Burrows, M.W. Christensen, S. Dipu, A. Gettelman, L.R. Leung, <span class="gissauthor">F. Tornow</span>, J. Quaas, A.C. Varble, H. Wang, K. Zhang, and Y. Zheng, 2024: <a href="https://pubs.giss.nasa.gov/abs/mu06200a.html">Can GCMs represent cloud adjustments to aerosol-cloud interactions?</a> <cite>Atmos. Chem. Phys.</cite>, submitted.</p>

